==================================================

A) Log Work Modal
- Manual entry (hours/minutes)
- Date picker
- Comment
- Remaining estimate preview

B) Timer UI
- Start / Stop button
- Live timer
- Auto-save on stop

C) Issue View
- Time log list
- Edit / Delete (based on permission)
- Total time summary

D) Timesheet Page
- Daily view
- Weekly view
- Filters:
  - Project
  - Issue Type
  - Date range

==================================================
STEP 7 — PERMISSIONS
==================================================

Implement guards:
- User can edit/delete own logs
- Admin can edit/delete all logs
- Backend enforced (not UI only)

==================================================
STEP 8 — JIRA BEHAVIOR RULES
==================================================

- Time logs never disappear silently
- Deleting a log restores remaining estimate
- Timer auto-stops on logout / refresh
- All updates are audit-safe

